OL,7,Fafter a man in his 40s died while
OL,8,Friding an e-scooter in
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FCarlton Road, St Ann's, shortly after
OL,12,F8pm on Thursday (23 May) after the man
OL,13,Fsustained a head injury.
OL,15,FHe rider, who was in his 40s, died at
OL,16,FQueen's Medical Centre on Friday
OL,17,Fevening (24 May).
