OL,6,FOfficers are continuing to investigate
OL,7,Fwhat caused the man to fall from the e-
OL,8,Fscooter and have asked witnesses or
OL,9,Fanyone with dash cam footage to come
OL,10,Fforward.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Liah Lane, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police's serious
OL,14,Fcollision investigation unit, said:
OL,15,F"This was a tragic incident and our
OL,16,Fthoughts are with the man's family at
OL,17,Fthis extremely difficult time.
