OL,6,F"We are continuing to appeal for
OL,7,Fwitnesses to come forward. If you saw
OL,8,Fwhat happened and have yet to get in
OL,9,Fcontact with us, please do not assume
OL,10,Fthat others have already told us what
OL,11,Fyou saw.
OL,13,F"We are working to build up a complete
OL,14,Fpicture of what happened. Whilst we do
OL,15,Fnot believe the e-scooter was involved
OL,16,Fin a collision with another vehicle,
OL,17,Fwe are keen to review any dashcam
OL,18,Ffootage recorded by passing vehicles
OL,19,Faround the time of the incident.
