OL,6,F"I would also like to thank the
OL,7,Fmembers of the public who came to the
OL,8,Finjured man's aid and stayed with him
OL,9,Funtil emergency services arrived. This
OL,10,Fwas a distressing incident for
OL,11,Feveryone involved and they acquitted
OL,12,Fthemselves admirably in a difficult
OL,13,Fsituation."
OL,15,FAnyone with information that could
OL,16,Fassist the investigation is asked to
OL,17,Fcall 101 quoting incident 641 of 23
OL,18,FMay 2024.
